Package: codex-history-viewer
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: wl-clipboard | xclip | xsel
Description: terminal viewer for codex-cli session history
 Full-screen terminal interface for browsing Codex CLI session history, with
 search, syntax-highlighted changes, and resume-command clipboard support.
 .
 This PPA package embeds the Node.js runtime used by the standalone upstream
 distribution and does not require the system Node.js package.
